title: Growing Mushrooms with things from Amazon.pdf
description:
Grow mushrooms right the first time. No more outdated methods from the 70s, grow chambers, or other overly complex methods. 

This two page guide will show you one way to cultivate mushrooms at home that works. It also comes with access to an online list of where to source everything mentioned so you don't have to guess if you have the right thing. 

This book is not for you if you like long drawn out scientific explanation about how everything is working. On the other hand it is for you if you like a step by step guide that fits on one sheet of paper. 

Growing mushrooms doesn't have to be complex or hard to do. Just follow this bulletproof, 5 step, at home guide to mushroom cultivation and you will get results

Printable Guide
